            </div></a><div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between px-6 text-black no-underline md:flex-nowrap md:px-4"><div class="order-1 mx-auto md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:flex md:w-full md:grow md:flex-col"><div class="block text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green md:text-left">魔术衣架节省空间坚固金属衣架衣柜壁橱收纳架节省空间衣架（12 件装）</div><div class="mt-2 block font-sans text-sm font-medium leading-5 text-gray-900 md:mx-0 md:mt-2">金属层叠衣架</div><div class="mt-2 hidden md:flex md:grow md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-sm font-medium md:text-xs">亚马逊</span><span class="text-base font-bold md:text-sm">29.99 美元</span><img class="mx-auto mt-0 inline" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime" width="42" height="15"></div><div class="my-0 text-center md:text-left"> <span class="text-sm font-bold line-through md:text-xs">$35.99</span><span class="text-base font-bold text-brand-green md:text-sm">节省 $6.00</span> </div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"><div class="h-11 hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="w-full rounded-md bg-brand-green py-3 text-center font-sans text-sm text-white"><span>现在去购物</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><img class="m-auto w-full rounded-md rounded-md border border-2 border-brand-green-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVVSYGJ3W6GYRESW0NP92Q44/images-2.fill.size_245x225.v1713551393.png" alt="层叠吊架" width="245" height="225" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-2 mt-2 hidden w-64 md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:block"><img class="m-auto w-full rounded-md border border-2 border-brand-green-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVVSYGJ3W6GYRESW0NP92Q44/images-2.fill.size_245x225.v1713551393.png" alt="层叠吊架" width="245" height="225" loading="lazy"></div><div class="ord